data.description: PRIVACY & VIEWS!!! This unique property has so many lovely features you don't see in many homes today, especially in Southern California, truly making it one-of-a-kind! Starting at the main street, the private driveway curves around the hill until you reach the top. The home is the only thing perched on top with nothing but 360 DEGREES OF PANORAMIC VIEWS. Once inside the double door entry, the space opens up to the large formal dining room to the left and with a step down on the right, your attention is immediately drawn to the huge BEAUTIFUL BEAMED VAUTED CEILINGS in the formal living room. Every room in this house has LARGE, OVERSIZED WINDOWS to capture the amazing views outside. This MASSIVE BRICK FIREPLACE is a feature of it's own as it is a TWO-WAY FIREPLACE and carries into the family room on the other side. Through to the kitchen, light birch colored cabinets and white tile counters compliment the laminate floors. The kitchen offers a ton of storage space and even some beautiful glass cabinets overhead. The adjacent family room offers the same beautiful beamed ceilings with floor to ceiling brick fireplace. The BUILT-IN WET BAR is an added bonus and nice touch! Down the hall, the master bedroom with ensuite bathroom offers a sliding glass door to the deck outside, and dual sinks and walk-in closet are always a must for the master bathroom. Once outside, the VIEWS ARE TRULY BREATHTAKING! There are very few homes in this city that can offer a property such as this and with a little TLC, this home can really shine again. If you're looking for a private, secluded home that isn't too far from the city, this is the home for you!
